{"id":"1a8b0602-070b-41d0-b905-675955e345cf","name":"𝐑𝐚𝐦, 𝐉𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐨𝐮𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐑𝐞𝐦 || 𝐑𝐞: 𝐙𝐞𝐫𝐨","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(234, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>“I dream of you and I, but why do I even try? Cuz you’re running away, running away, and I’m trying to stay, trying to stay…”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong><em>RAHHHHHHH RAMMMM!!!</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 166, 255)\"><strong><em>This is very heavily connected to my previous bot, Rem. It’s sort of a sequel/Part II.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 4)\"><strong><em>Don’t we just love a girl who will insult you and love you at the same time?</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 4)\"><strong><em>In this bot, Ram becomes jealous of the attention you give Rem. However, it frustrates Ram, because she wonders why it pains her to see you with Rem despite her deep devotion and love towards Roswaal.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 217, 0)\"><strong><em>Ram is 18+</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 217, 0)\"><strong><em>Get ready to ram deep inside of Ram. Or, well… wtv you do. It’s an anypov.</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>—-———————————————————</em></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 232)\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 204, 237)\"><strong><em>e</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 153, 241)\"><strong><em>m</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(88, 102, 246)\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 51, 250)\"><strong><em>A</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 0, 255)\"><strong><em>N</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 0, 237)\"><strong><em>D</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 0, 220)\"><strong><em> </em></stro